We are creating a online website for managing a library. To accomplish this we are using django, bootstrap, html amd css.
The basic users of the Library Mangement system will be a Admin and the Students.
The features available to the admin will be:
- Adding/Deleting a Book
- Adding/deleting a Student
- Viewing a/all Books/Student
- Issuing/Returning a book
- Viewing every issued books by the students
The features available to the students will be:
- Viewing/Editing their profile
- Info(Maybe a sneak preview) of the books
- View their issued books
